        "Ja-Ela Police Station Officer-in-Charge R. M. G. D. Ratnayake led by Inspector Sampath Dissanayake in charge of the Complaints Division, Police Sergeant (35599) Vanninayake and Police Constable (24346) Silva are conducting further investigations."
